def main():
    n = int(input())
    values = [int(x) for x in input().split()]
    costs = [int(x) for x in input().split()]
    max_value = 0
    for i in range(1, 2 ** n):
        value = 0
        cost = 0
        for j in range(n):
            if ((i >> j) & 1):
                value += values[j]
                cost += costs[j]
        max_value = max(max_value, value - cost)
    print(max_value)  # noqa: E999


if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()

import math


N = int(input())  # データ数
data = [int(input()) for _ in range(N)]  # データ

# 平均
mean = sum(data) / N
# 分散
variance = sum([(x - mean) ** 2 for x in data]) / N
# 標準偏差
stdev = math.sqrt(variance)

print(variance)
print(stdev)
